    description: 'Hirado Single Bed with Storage is a masterfully engineered sleep solution designed to introduce architectural clarity and a bright, orderly energy to contemporary bedrooms or professional studio apartments. Piece features a high-strength structural framework meticulously crafted from premium Laminated Board, ensuring exceptional structural integrity and a professional aesthetic for daily residential use. Design is distinguished by its uniform Oak finish, offering a prestigious tactile sense of luxury while celebrating the soft, natural movement of wood grain across its expansive surfaces. Technical configuration incorporates a specialized integrated storage system within the bed base and side rail, providing a durable platform for high-capacity professional organization of linens and personal essentials. Architectural profile maintains a grounded, authoritative presence while maximizing functional utility within its optimized footprint, featuring a 1900mm side rail for enhanced stability. With an ergonomic headboard and a specific footboard height, it provides a prestigious and stable platform for a standard mattress, radiating a fresh, modern energy throughout the room. Overall look harmonizes functional durability with a sophisticated low-profile silhouette, serving as an ideal centerpiece for professional environments that value material excellence and expert craftsmanship.',
