    description: 'Hirado 1.5m tv cabinet in Natural colour leg, Oak colour top and White colour drawer. Hirado 1.5m TV Cabinet is a masterfully engineered media solution designed to introduce architectural clarity and a bright, energetic atmosphere to contemporary living environments. Piece features a high-strength structural framework supported by robust, tapered legs meticulously crafted from Solid Malaysian Oak in a soft Natural finish, ensuring exceptional structural integrity and a professional aesthetic. Design is distinguished by its sophisticated dual-tone body, pairing a warm Oak frame with precision-fitted doors in a crisp White finish to offer a prestigious tactile sense of luxury and a refined visual contrast. Technical configuration incorporates a specialized storage system with smooth-operating doors, providing a durable and organized platform for essential electronics and professional organizational needs. Architectural profile maintains a grounded, authoritative presence while maximizing floor efficiency within its specialized W1500mm footprint. With an ergonomic height, it provides a prestigious and stable platform for widescreen displays and curated decorative arrangements, radiating a serene atmospheric energy throughout the room. Overall look harmonizes traditional wood artistry with a clean, contemporary color palette, serving as an ideal centerpiece for spaces that value architectural integrity and material excellence.',
