    description: 'Lome 1.65m TV Cabinet is a masterfully engineered media solution designed to introduce architectural clarity and a bright, airy energy to contemporary living environments. Piece features a high-strength structural framework supported by robust, tapered legs meticulously crafted from Solid Malaysian Oak in a soft Natural finish, ensuring exceptional structural integrity and a professional aesthetic. Design is distinguished by its premium Laminated Board body in a warm Oak finish, offering a prestigious tactile sense of luxury while celebrating the soft, natural appearance of wood grain through its clean linear profile. Technical configuration incorporates a specialized multi-compartment storage system with precision-fitted doors and open shelving, providing a durable platform for media consoles and high-end electronics. Architectural profile maintains a grounded, authoritative presence while maximizing floor efficiency within its specialized footprint. With an ergonomic height, it provides a prestigious and stable platform for widescreen displays and curated decorative arrangements, radiating a serene atmospheric energy throughout the room. Overall look harmonizes traditional wood artistry with a sleek, modern silhouette, serving as an ideal centerpiece for professional environments that value material excellence and expert craftsmanship.',
