    description: 'Lome 6 drawer dresser in Natural colour leg, Oak colour top. Lome 6 Drawer Dresser is a masterfully engineered storage solution designed to introduce architectural clarity and a bright, organic energy to expansive contemporary bedrooms or professional dressing areas. Piece features a high-strength structural framework supported by robust legs meticulously crafted from Solid Malaysian Oak in a natural finish, ensuring exceptional structural integrity and a professional aesthetic. Design is distinguished by its premium Laminated Board body in a warm oak finish, offering a prestigious tactile sense of luxury while celebrating soft, natural timber textures through its widened horizontal profile. Technical configuration incorporates a specialized six-tier drawer system with precision-fitted glides and sleek, integrated handles, providing a durable platform for professional organization and daily essentials. Architectural profile maintains a grounded, authoritative presence while maximizing storage capacity within its substantial W1485mm x D400mm footprint. With a functional H800mm height, it provides a prestigious and stable platform for curated displays and grooming accessories, radiating a fresh, modern energy throughout the room. Overall look harmonizes traditional wood artistry with a clean, minimalist silhouette, serving as an ideal centerpiece for professional environments that value material excellence and expert craftsmanship.',
