    description: 'Lome 1.6m Sideboard is a masterfully engineered storage solution designed to introduce architectural clarity and a bright, airy energy to contemporary living or office environments. Piece features a high-strength structural framework supported by robust legs meticulously crafted from Solid Malaysian Oak in a Natural finish, ensuring exceptional structural integrity and a professional aesthetic. Design is distinguished by its premium Laminated Board body in a warm Oak finish, offering a prestigious tactile sense of luxury while celebrating the soft, natural appearance of wood grain through its elongated linear profile. Technical configuration incorporates a specialized multi-compartment storage system with precision-fitted doors and integrated internal shelving, providing a durable platform for professional organization and curated displays. Architectural profile maintains a grounded, authoritative presence while maximizing storage capacity within its generous W1600mm x D400mm footprint. With an ergonomic H800mm height, it provides a prestigious and stable platform for decorative arrangements and media accessories, radiating a serene atmospheric energy throughout the room. Overall look harmonizes traditional wood artistry with a clean, modern silhouette, serving as an ideal centerpiece for professional environments that value material excellence and expert craftsmanship.',
