    description: 'Kohana 1.4m Bench is a masterfully engineered seating solution designed to introduce architectural clarity and a bright, airy energy to modern dining or entryway environments. Piece features an exposed architectural framework supported by robust, cylindrical legs meticulously crafted from Solid Malaysian Oak, ensuring exceptional structural integrity and a professional aesthetic. Seating surface consists of precision-finished solid timber slats, celebrating the organic beauty of the wood grain while offering a prestigious tactile sense of luxury. Design is defined by its clean, linear silhouette and an open-frame profile that incorporates a stabilizing cross-bar system for enhanced durability. Architectural profile maintains a light floor presence while offering a sense of sculptural clarity suitable for boutique dining rooms or creative residential offices. Overall look radiates a timeless sophistication with a coastal edge, serving as an ideal centerpiece for professional environments that value material excellence and expert craftsmanship.',
